Calligra Suite is a set of applications written to help you to accomplish your
work. Calligra Office includes efficient and capable office components:
  Words for text processing.
  Sheets for computations.
  Stage for presentations.
  Plan for planning.
  Flow for flowcharts.
  Kexi for database creation.
  Calligra Art

Calligra offers cutting edge applications for artists to work on 2D drawings and
illustrations:
  Krita for painting and raster drawing.
  Karbon for vector graphics.
